name: A1 filter
description:
It kind of makes things seem like A-1 Pictures made them.

Made by extracting a auto Block Weight merge of detailedproject4 (dpep4) and Animelike2.5D found here against dpep4 as a LoRA. It's an extracted lora so it's not terribly high quality but I just wanted to make it as an experiment.
